This paper is about instance segmentation, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a new method for instance segmentation, which involves classification and regression, making it relevant to sub-categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses optimization and sampling techniques, which are relevant to sub-categories such as cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
